::: Set looked around, and then at Ominous who rested comfortably in the 
Brig. :::

::: set ::: Well, I got to go now, and take over this rock. You stay here.

~~~~~~~~

::: Hell Beast, followed by Inferno, Rampage, Transanulas, Marine, Black 
Aracnia, Pheniox, Gremlin, and Jackle left the base and waited for Shuko. He 
left Scourge and Tankkor at the base, and Vuloris and his team at the base. 
He hoped Double Puch and his team would show up too. :::

::: Black Aracnia ::: So, today we kill that Maximals. I knew I was going to 
have a headache.

~~~~~~~~~~

::: Megatron looks to his scanners ::: Well, if therre going to join 
forces....

::: Waspinator ::: Are we going to attack?

::: Megatron ::: Lets just watch the show and see what happens.
